title: Pro Photo West Magazine Fall 2014 ~ Frank Doorhof
description:
You know what they say: good things come to those who wait. The Pro Photo West Fall 2014 issue is finally here and it is packed with reviews, tutorials, interviews, and insights.

In the Winter issue you will also discover:
- An exclusive interview with Frank Doorhof
- A tutorial on how to be unique by Judy Host
- An exclusive interview with Joey Terrill
- A photokina report with Martin Hausler
- A first look at Honey Grids by Alex Munoz
- A full review of the Sigma Dp2 by Janet Bark
- A first look at the Pixel Mago
- And so much more
